stateDiagram
  direction TB
  [*] --> ExtractToken
  ExtractToken --> ValidateToken: call auth service
  ValidateToken --> ValidateRole:token valid
  ValidateRole --> Authorized:allowed
  ValidateRole --> Forbidden:denied
  ValidateToken --> Unauthorized:token invalid or expired
  Authorized --> ForwardRequest
  ForwardRequest --> [*]
  Forbidden --> [*]
  Unauthorized --> [*]